<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <% include ../../../partials/header.ejs %>

 <script>
$(document).ready(function() {

  $('#buttonCreateProject').click(function() {

    $("#successCreateProject").addClass('hide-element');
    $('#outputCreateProject').text('Running command in playground, one moment...');
    $("outputCreateProject").css("text-decoration", "blink");

    $.ajax({
      type: "GET",
      url: "/playgound-api/java/createproject",
      dataType: "text"
    }).done (function (data) {
      $("#successCreateProject").removeClass('hide-element');
      $("#outputCreateProject").css("text-decoration", "none");
      $('#outputCreateProject').text(data);
    });
  });
});

</script>

</head>

<body>

  <% include ../../../partials/header-playground-java.ejs %>

<!-- Tutorial steps -->
<div class="container">

  <p class="mt-3">The <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> is a virtual cloud-based development environment with Java and Maven installed.
    You can learn how to create Java apps for Marketing Cloud right within your browser. No need to install anything on your computer!</p>

  <p class="mt-3">We've already created an empty <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> for you.</p>
    
  <p class="mt-3">Let's use the playground to create a simple Java app that uses the <a href="http://salesforce-marketingcloud.github.io/FuelSDK-Java/" target="_blank">Marketing Cloud Java SDK</a> to send a test e-mail to a contact and check status of the e-mail.</p>

  <!-- Step 1 -->
  <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-block">
        <div class="card-header text-white" style="background-color: #00AA9E;">Step 1.1: Create a Maven project in the playground</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Click <strong>Run Command</strong> to create a new Java Maven project in the playground. </p>
            <pre style="max-height: 30em" data-src="/code-snippets/java/mvn-newproject.sh"></pre>
            <button id="buttonCreateProject" class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">Run command</button>
            <div class="card mt-3">
              <div class="card-header"><small>CONSOLE OUTPUT</small></div>
              <pre class="m-2">
                <code id="outputCreateProject" class="language-bash">Nothing yet. Click 'Run Command' to see results.</code>
              </pre>
            </div>

            <div id="successCreateProject" class="hide-element">
              <p class="card-text mt-3"><span class="fa fa-star text-success"></span>&nbsp;You have sucessfully created a new Java Maven project in the playground!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="container text-center">
  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-md m-4 button-fixed-width-300 active" style="text-align:center" href="/sdks/playground/java-play-2">Go to step 2</a>
</div>

<% include ../../../partials/footer.ejs %>

</body>
</html>